<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.10.7">
<l>tirutta ṉaitticai nāṉmukaṉ tantaiyait tēva tēvaṉai mūvaril muṉṉiya</l>
<l>virutta ṉaiviḷaṅ kumcuṭarc cōtiyai viṇṇai maṇṇiṉaik kaṇṇutal kūṭiya</l>
<l>arutta ṉaiyari yaippari kīṟiya vappa ṉaiya<supplied>p</supplied>pi lāraḻa lāyniṉṟa</l>
<l>karutta ṉaikaḷi vaṇṭaṟai yumpoḻil kaṇṇa maṅkaiyuḷ kaṇṭukoṇ ṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I saw for myself in Kaṇṇamaṅkai, with groves where drunken bees hum,</l>
<l rend="indent">[the one who is]</l>
<l>Of sacred waters, the father of him who faces the four directions,</l>
<l rend="indent">god of gods, the ancient who endures among the Three,</l>
<l>The splendor of the sun that shines, heaven and earth,</l>
<l rend="indent">the one on whose half the forehead-eyed [god] is joined,</l>
<l>A lion, [our] father who split the horse, and the creator</l>
<l rend="indent">who endures as the rare fire in the ocean.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
